00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:14,140
I've long heard about you, Mr. Zhang.

301
00:18:14,579 --> 00:18:15,980
It's just that with the audit work,

302
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:17,240
I've been swamped nonstop,

303
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,420
otherwise, I'd have reached out sooner.

304
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:21,819
You've got a way with words.

305
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:23,920
Ms. Miao.

306
00:18:24,519 --> 00:18:25,160
Have we

307
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:26,880
met somewhere before?

308
00:18:28,039 --> 00:18:29,279
You still remember me, Mr. Zhang?

309
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:30,839
I grew up

310
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:31,859
with Chen Yi.

311
00:18:32,559 --> 00:18:33,960
I used to hang around District 7

312
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:34,740
waiting for him to get off work.

313
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:36,240
If I'd known you recognized me,

314
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,319
I'd have changed

315
00:18:37,539 --> 00:18:38,640
out of this overly formal outfit.

316
00:18:39,819 --> 00:18:40,259
Ms. Miao,

317
00:18:40,259 --> 00:18:41,400
you're quite a character.

318
00:18:41,759 --> 00:18:42,599
And Chen Yi

319
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,519
is quite a character too.

320
00:18:45,099 --> 00:18:46,299
You and your brother

321
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:49,220
are truly fascinating.

322
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,380
I heard

323
00:18:54,039 --> 00:18:55,259
you studied in Haicheng

324
00:18:55,559 --> 00:18:56,759
for years.

325
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:58,940
Haicheng's far more

326
00:18:59,559 --> 00:19:00,819
developed than Vineton.

327
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:03,500
What brought you back?

328
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,759
I've always thought

329
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,059
Vineton's better, actually.

330
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:12,960
Mr. Zhang.

331
00:19:18,759 --> 00:19:19,519
Chen Yi's here.

332
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:22,039
Send him in.

333
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:30,299
Mr. Zhang.

334
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,420
Looks like I came at a bad time.

335
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:38,259
Nonsense.

336
00:19:39,099 --> 00:19:40,019
Your sister's right here.

337
00:19:40,559 --> 00:19:40,920
Have a seat.

338
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,420
You flatter me, Mr. Zhang.

339
00:19:45,240 --> 00:19:46,259
We only shared a place

340
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:47,420
for a couple of years.

341
00:19:48,259 --> 00:19:49,099
She's not my sister.

342
00:19:52,599 --> 00:19:53,559
Why can't you talk properly

343
00:19:53,559 --> 00:19:54,640
the second you walk in here?

344
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:56,839
Ms. Miao,

345
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,019
don't take his words to heart.

346
00:20:03,539 --> 00:20:04,900
Still, after all these

347
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:07,539
twists and turns, here we are,

348
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:09,460
sitting at the same table,

349
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:10,480
all working at Haoyun.

350
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:12,900
It's fate, really.

351
00:20:14,460 --> 00:20:15,420
The smooth delivery

352
00:20:17,359 --> 00:20:18,539
of our project

353
00:20:21,039 --> 00:20:22,000
depends on you two.

354
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:24,859
That's a stretch, Mr. Zhang.

355
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:26,940
We're all just regular staff here.

356
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:28,900
It's up to you as our supervisor

357
00:20:29,299 --> 00:20:30,099
to lead us to success.

358
00:20:34,519 --> 00:20:35,599
So what if you're just staff?

359
00:20:36,819 --> 00:20:37,539
The two of you

360
00:20:38,279 --> 00:20:39,819
are the most vital people

361
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:41,500
to Haoyun, and to me.

362
00:20:43,279 --> 00:20:44,180
Ms. Miao, you know,

363
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,619
there was a weak link

364
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:48,500
in our new logistics chain.

365
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,460
But thanks to your brother,

366
00:20:51,339 --> 00:20:52,140
we closed

367
00:20:52,539 --> 00:20:54,140
the whole loop seamlessly.

368
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:55,740
Don't be misled

369
00:20:55,740 --> 00:20:56,700
by his humble remarks.

370
00:20:58,059 --> 00:20:59,160
He's tremendously talented.

371
00:21:02,099 --> 00:21:02,440
Oh right,

372
00:21:03,119 --> 00:21:03,700
I almost forgot.

373
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,279
Those pastries

374
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,720
over there are a special gift

375
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,680
for you from Mr. Li.

376
00:21:09,259 --> 00:21:11,140
He stressed over and over

377
00:21:11,359 --> 00:21:12,700
that since you're in charge

378
00:21:13,319 --> 00:21:14,359
of this run,

379
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:16,160
you need to stay on top of it,

380
00:21:16,619 --> 00:21:17,740
make the rounds yourself.

381
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:18,900
Once

382
00:21:19,019 --> 00:21:19,940
this business trip wraps up,

383
00:21:20,319 --> 00:21:21,519
you can have extra annual leave.

384
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:22,839
Take your sister

385
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:24,339
to check out

386
00:21:24,819 --> 00:21:25,880
Vineton's new landmarks.

387
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:28,079
Mr. Zhang,

388
00:21:29,339 --> 00:21:30,539
if I'm not mistaken,

389
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,660
the new logistics route you mentioned

390
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:33,859
is the one heading to Southeast Asia.

391
00:21:44,819 --> 00:21:45,740
That's correct.

392
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:46,920
You've done your homework,

393
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,099
Ms. Miao.

394
00:21:49,059 --> 00:21:49,539
Chen Yi,

395
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:51,900
you better step it up.

396
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:54,039
Make sure this route

397
00:21:54,140 --> 00:21:54,839
is fully up

398
00:21:55,079 --> 00:21:55,759
and running without hiccups.

399
00:21:57,420 --> 00:21:57,740
If you

400
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:59,299
keep dragging your feet,

401
00:22:00,339 --> 00:22:00,980
who knows how long

402
00:22:00,980 --> 00:22:02,140
your sister will have to stay at Haoyun.

403
00:22:07,839 --> 00:22:08,180
Alright.

404
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:10,339
Kao's already

405
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:11,539
notified me.

406
00:22:13,039 --> 00:22:13,599
Really?

407
00:22:16,859 --> 00:22:17,519
That's great.

408
00:22:18,319 --> 00:22:19,220
Once you're over there,

409
00:22:19,220 --> 00:22:20,420
you can catch up with them.

410
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:22,980
Ms. Miao,

411
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:25,859
if you're swamped tonight,

412
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,140
you may leave early.

413
00:22:28,839 --> 00:22:30,240
This dinner was put together

414
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:31,960
on rather short notice.

415
00:22:32,519 --> 00:22:33,940
I'll host you both properly another time.

416
00:22:35,539 --> 00:22:35,940
Sounds great.

417
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,640
I'll look forward to hearing from you.

418
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:38,839
But it's rather inconvenient

419
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,380
commuting back downtown this late,

420
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,420
so I'll wait for my brother.

421
00:22:46,359 --> 00:22:46,619
Alright.

422
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,779
That's safer.

423
00:22:50,980 --> 00:22:52,140
Come on, a toast to you two.

424
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:54,619
Just toast with water.

425
00:22:54,779 --> 00:22:55,180
Cheers.

426
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:21,579
Why did you come?

427
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:23,519
You know how he is.

428
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,759
You're already in charge

429
00:23:26,759 --> 00:23:27,619
of Haoyun's audit.

430
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:28,599
What would you do

431
00:23:28,599 --> 00:23:29,279
if he'd made any unreasonable requests

432
00:23:29,279 --> 00:23:29,900
to you just now?

433
00:23:36,819 --> 00:23:37,240
Also,

434
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,619
you shouldn't

435
00:23:39,619 --> 00:23:40,579
let him associate you with me.

436
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,259
He sent for me tonight,

437
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,180
which means he already knows

438
00:23:45,180 --> 00:23:45,920
about us.

439
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:47,759
No point hiding it.

440
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:51,019
What good could

441
00:23:51,740 --> 00:23:52,619
a mere auditor like me

442
00:23:52,619 --> 00:23:53,740
be to Zhang Bin?

443
00:23:55,519 --> 00:23:56,420
You've been out in the world for years,

444
00:23:56,420 --> 00:23:57,180
you should know

445
00:23:58,119 --> 00:23:59,240
he's just using me

446
00:23:59,279 --> 00:24:00,400
as bait to toy with you.

447
00:25:19,279 --> 00:25:19,960
What are you doing?

448
00:25:21,599 --> 00:25:22,940
Nothing. Just packing up.

449
00:25:26,539 --> 00:25:27,259
It's getting cold.

450
00:25:27,579 --> 00:25:28,400
Dry your hair.

451
00:25:41,539 --> 00:25:42,240
What are you doing?

452
00:25:51,839 --> 00:25:52,420
Where are you going?

453
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,079
Autumn's already here in Vineton.

454
00:25:54,579 --> 00:25:55,839
Why pack summer clothes?

455
00:26:00,319 --> 00:26:01,480
Freight department sent me on a business trip.

456
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:04,000
Where exactly?

457
00:26:04,819 --> 00:26:05,220
Gangcheng.

458
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:06,920
Only two or three days.

459
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,000
Chen Yi,

460
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:11,980
you promised you'd never lie to me,

461
00:26:11,980 --> 00:26:12,440
didn't you?

462
00:26:16,359 --> 00:26:17,359
Zhang Bin sent you?

463
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:18,920
Who's Kao you mentioned

464
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:19,500
that night?

465
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,000
Are you going to Jinguo?

466
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:31,180
Owen.

467
00:26:32,119 --> 00:26:32,839
How did you find out?

468
00:26:33,839 --> 00:26:34,480
This is what you've been

469
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:35,220
trying to hide from me,

470
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:35,640
isn't it?

471
00:26:35,859 --> 00:26:36,680
Zhang Bin told you?

472
00:26:36,819 --> 00:26:37,799
You're not going anywhere tomorrow.

473
00:26:42,299 --> 00:26:43,160
There are things

474
00:26:43,859 --> 00:26:44,519
you're better off not knowing.

475
00:26:53,460 --> 00:26:54,539
Miao Jing, what are you doing now?

476
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,619
I'm sleeping here tonight.

477
00:27:12,299 --> 00:27:12,859
Chen Yi.

478
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,700
Whatever you've been through,

479
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:17,299
that's in the past.

480
00:27:17,299 --> 00:27:18,359
I don't want to pry.

481
00:27:20,339 --> 00:27:21,099
But tomorrow,

482
00:27:22,059 --> 00:27:23,000
you're not going anywhere.

483
00:27:23,279 --> 00:27:24,240
It's not what you think.

484
00:27:29,559 --> 00:27:30,680
I was in Jinguo those years,

485
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:33,920
but I knew full well

486
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:34,480
what to do

487
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:34,920
and what not to.

488
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:35,539
I trust you.

489
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,240
So can you not go tomorrow?

490
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,039
I'll be back soon.

491
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,319
I heard that line

492
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,779
six years ago.

493
00:28:26,119 --> 00:28:27,619
My eyelid's been twitching all day.

494
00:28:28,279 --> 00:28:29,420
Can you just not go?

495
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,140
I'll be back to stay with you

496
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,019
before scores come out tomorrow.

497
00:28:36,519 --> 00:28:36,960
Pinky swear?

498
00:28:41,019 --> 00:28:42,480
Pinky swear, cross my heart,

499
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:43,720
a hundred years, no take-backs.

500
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:45,480
Break it, we're done forever.

501
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:52,980
You're not going anywhere.

502
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,099
Try me.

503
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:01,819
Chen Yi.

504
00:31:06,779 --> 00:31:08,000
So you're the famous Chen Yi.

505
00:31:09,859 --> 00:31:11,339
A border runner.

506
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:13,579
Used to

507
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,779
work under Kao, huh?

508
00:31:16,759 --> 00:31:17,559
Is it because

509
00:31:17,559 --> 00:31:18,980
you pulled some big job before

510
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,740
that you can't even go through customs?

511
00:31:21,380 --> 00:31:22,980
Gotta take a boat to Gangcheng

512
00:31:23,299 --> 00:31:24,140
and then to Jinguo.

513
00:31:24,579 --> 00:31:25,680
It's bumpy as hell.

514
00:31:26,359 --> 00:31:27,119
Right?

515
00:31:31,019 --> 00:31:31,839
Are those goods

516
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:33,279
hot?

517
00:31:34,900 --> 00:31:36,079
Don't kid me.

518
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,720
How would I know

519
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:39,339
what the boss is shipping?

520
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:41,759
I'm just a hired hand.

521
00:31:42,799 --> 00:31:43,400
Biao.

522
00:31:50,220 --> 00:31:50,859
Don't mind it.

523
00:31:51,319 --> 00:31:52,119
Routine body search.

524
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,380
You'll get it back when we dock.

525
00:31:58,819 --> 00:31:59,460
The boat will

526
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:00,920
reach Gangcheng in forty minutes.

527
00:32:01,259 --> 00:32:02,259
I was told to move those goods

528
00:32:02,259 --> 00:32:02,900
to Jinguo.

529
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,119
What do you mean?

530
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:08,559
The goods aren't on it?

531
00:32:10,140 --> 00:32:10,920
Of course not.

532
00:32:11,559 --> 00:32:13,240
The goods already made it to Gangcheng

533
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,220
by truck.

534
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:16,579
Mr. Chen,

535
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:18,200
shall we go?

536
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:22,400
This isn't what we

537
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,000
agreed on.

538
00:32:46,079 --> 00:32:46,759
Hello?

539
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:47,819
I'd like to report a crime.

540
00:32:49,900 --> 00:32:51,000
A group of men are gearing up for a fight.

541
00:32:52,059 --> 00:32:53,359
I don't have many details,

542
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,279
only the license plate

543
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,220
and one man's name.

544
00:32:58,759 --> 00:32:59,579
The plate is

545
00:33:00,299 --> 00:33:01,660
Teng SF

546
00:33:02,259 --> 00:33:03,140
A302

547
00:33:04,579 --> 00:33:05,359
The name is

548
00:33:07,460 --> 00:33:07,960
Chen Yi.

549
00:33:11,039 --> 00:33:12,539
Come on, Chen Yi. Stop stalling.

550
00:33:13,039 --> 00:33:13,799
Wait any longer,

551
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:14,640
the tide's gonna rise,

552
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:15,660
and we won't be able to leave.

553
00:33:20,279 --> 00:33:21,200
I'm not going without the cargo.

554
00:33:23,740 --> 00:33:25,140
A real border runner, huh?

555
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:26,839
Got some nerve.

556
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:29,619
I don't care what you're thinking.

557
00:33:30,359 --> 00:33:31,779
But I've got orders from above,

558
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:33,119
and I'm seeing this through.

559
00:33:34,539 --> 00:33:35,740
I said I'd get you there.

560
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,220
In half an hour,

561
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:38,180
you'll be there.

562
00:33:48,180 --> 00:33:48,799
You boss

563
00:33:48,799 --> 00:33:50,079
watches too many gangster movies,

564
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,640
letting you scumbags

565
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:53,759
run your mouths nonstop.

566
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:03,740
Cops!

567
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,099
Stay where you are! Don't move!

568
00:34:11,039 --> 00:34:11,679
Police!

569
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,239
Don't move!

570
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:21,360
We suspect you of illegal fishing.

571
00:34:22,639 --> 00:34:23,519
Show me your IDs.

572
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:24,639
IDs.

573
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:44,500
What are you guys

574
00:34:45,820 --> 00:34:46,639
doing huddled here?

575
00:34:49,460 --> 00:34:49,840
I...

576
00:34:54,039 --> 00:34:54,500
Officer,

577
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,840
these are cargo vessels from Gangcheng.

578
00:34:57,199 --> 00:34:58,039
I'm a logistics firm's

579
00:34:58,039 --> 00:34:58,719
freight manager.

580
00:34:59,159 --> 00:35:00,480
I just came to check the boats tonight,

581
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:01,860
nothing else.

582
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:07,860
Is that true?

583
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,980
Yes, absolutely.

584
00:35:15,639 --> 00:35:16,639
No one leaves.

585
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:18,800
We'll take detailed statements.

586
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:22,699
Officer, they're from Gangcheng,

587
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:25,059
cargo boat crews.

588
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,280
I work for a logistics firm,

589
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,079
freight manager.

590
00:35:27,519 --> 00:35:28,280
Just came

591
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,739
to inspect the boats.

592
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:33,300
So can we

593
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,239
go now?

594
00:35:34,679 --> 00:35:35,059
Biao.

595
00:35:35,599 --> 00:35:35,960
Let's go.

596
00:35:39,519 --> 00:35:39,920
Get in the car.

597
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:40,519
Alright.

598
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:42,099
Get in.

599
00:35:53,139 --> 00:35:54,559
Their goods aren't even on the boat.

600
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,420
This trip was just a test.

601
00:35:56,599 --> 00:35:57,480
They're even wary of me.

602
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,639
They laid a smokescreen,

603
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,500
and we'll play it by ear.

604
00:36:04,199 --> 00:36:05,159
The task force

605
00:36:06,019 --> 00:36:07,239
will take over.

606
00:36:10,619 --> 00:36:11,699
They'll likely

607
00:36:12,139 --> 00:36:12,639
assume

608
00:36:12,639 --> 00:36:14,119
we're focusing all our efforts

609
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,659
on the water route.

610
00:36:16,099 --> 00:36:16,659
So

611
00:36:17,139 --> 00:36:18,539
they're far more likely

612
00:36:18,539 --> 00:36:19,699
to move goods

613
00:36:20,199 --> 00:36:20,900
via land routes next.

614
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:22,639
We don't mind spooking them.

615
00:36:23,079 --> 00:36:24,179
We fear they'll never move.

616
00:36:28,179 --> 00:36:29,679
Wasn't the op scheduled for 9:30 PM?

617
00:36:30,199 --> 00:36:31,760
Why'd you guys show up early?

618
00:36:36,260 --> 00:36:37,019
Someone called it in,

619
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,480
said you were here

620
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,559
involved in a fight.

621
00:36:43,739 --> 00:36:44,460
Miao Jing made the call.

622
00:36:48,599 --> 00:36:49,559
She reported you

623
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:50,840
and have us bring you in.

624
00:36:51,079 --> 00:36:51,719
You're not scared?

625
00:36:53,579 --> 00:36:54,920
If she'd dialed 110,

626
00:36:55,099 --> 00:36:55,800
I wouldn't be

627
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:57,000
riding in your car right now.

628
00:36:58,079 --> 00:36:59,639
She phoned our captain privately.

629
00:37:00,219 --> 00:37:00,719
She wouldn't

630
00:37:00,719 --> 00:37:01,780
actually try to get me locked up.

631
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,019
Boy,

632
00:37:06,239 --> 00:37:07,139
you're lucky.

633
00:37:09,219 --> 00:37:10,300
She was scared for you.

634
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:12,980
Go thank her when you get back.

635
00:37:13,719 --> 00:37:14,139
Let's go.

636
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,000
Miao Jing.

637
00:38:06,019 --> 00:38:06,619
Miao Jing.

638
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:17,320
Miao Jing.

639
00:38:21,119 --> 00:38:21,679
Miao Jing.

640
00:39:00,039 --> 00:39:00,820
It's you?

641
00:39:16,300 --> 00:39:16,800
This way.

642
00:39:20,599 --> 00:39:21,239
Where's Xiao Yu?

643
00:39:22,159 --> 00:39:23,079
Disappointed to see me?

644
00:39:24,019 --> 00:39:25,079
Just surprised.

645
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:27,860
I helped her

646
00:39:27,860 --> 00:39:29,019
fix some data stuff

647
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,159
so she'd send me

648
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,440
to pick you up.

649
00:39:31,900 --> 00:39:33,059
That's not a good deal.

650
00:39:33,699 --> 00:39:35,420
Your work sense is slipping?

651
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:38,440
This is overdelivering.

652
00:39:41,019 --> 00:39:41,500
Here.

653
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,280
How long are you planning to stay here?

654
00:39:50,500 --> 00:39:51,699
I'll be here

655
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:52,599
until I head back to Haicheng.

656
00:39:53,099 --> 00:39:54,420
I'm sure everyone's happy about that.

657
00:39:56,019 --> 00:39:57,340
Xiao Yu and Ma Yang are on that side.

658
00:39:57,900 --> 00:39:58,519
I'm on this side.

659
00:40:00,260 --> 00:40:01,179
We're all on the same floor.

660
00:40:04,059 --> 00:40:04,960
Reach out if you need anything.

661
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:07,239
Thanks.

662
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:08,460
Get some rest.

663
00:40:24,739 --> 00:40:25,380
Chen Yi.

664
00:40:26,579 --> 00:40:27,699
If today was our

665
00:40:27,699 --> 00:40:28,659
last day together,

666
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,920
what would you wanna do?

667
00:40:59,599 --> 00:41:00,539
I brought you some fruit.

668
00:41:23,699 --> 00:41:24,719
Miao Jing's not home?

669
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:26,400
Work's busy.

670
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:27,280
She's on a business trip.

671
00:41:30,199 --> 00:41:30,820
I meant to stop by

672
00:41:30,820 --> 00:41:32,079
a couple days ago,

673
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:33,559
but Xiaobao had a fever,

674
00:41:33,559 --> 00:41:34,460
so I couldn't get away.

675
00:41:36,099 --> 00:41:36,840
Is he feeling better now?

676
00:41:38,519 --> 00:41:38,980
Much better.

677
00:41:43,219 --> 00:41:43,739
Want some noodles?

678
00:41:46,239 --> 00:41:46,840
No, thanks.

679
00:41:50,039 --> 00:41:50,639
Yi.

680
00:41:51,559 --> 00:41:53,079
Do you remember what you used to say?

681
00:41:53,340 --> 00:41:54,260
That you hated it when girls

682
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:54,960
came into your kitchen.

683
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,079
What brings you here?

684
00:41:56,619 --> 00:41:57,400
Is something

685
00:41:57,579 --> 00:41:58,320
going on at home?

686
00:42:02,519 --> 00:42:02,940
No.

687
00:42:04,420 --> 00:42:05,820
I came to ask you something.

688
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,460
On Bo's wedding day,

689
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:10,519
you wanted to stand beside Miao Jing,

690
00:42:10,519 --> 00:42:11,039
didn't you?
